00:18:46.720 --> 00:18:47.880
malamang itinago niya muna ang mga iyon.

00:18:48.359 --> 00:18:50.960
Naroon ang lahat ng mahahalagang palamuti at alahas

00:18:51.400 --> 00:18:52.440
at isinaalang-alang.

